{"type": "article", "id": 24927, "title": "黄铜怎么用才不浮夸？慕尼黑这间酒吧来教你", "description": "擅用黄铜的英国设计师 Tom Dixon 认为，黄铜最近很流行有可能是因其有一种“怀旧的舒适”的特质。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-05T07:00:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 14837, "name": "酒吧设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 249, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162953zZgsaB6O5vXFewiY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>黄铜最近很流行。</p>\n<p>我们不久前曾介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/24471.html\">悉尼 Sonama Bakery 烘焙店</a>，一条从入口处的地面延伸至面包柜台的黄铜带就成为了设计的点睛之笔；去年年底曾报道的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19918.html\">布拉格公寓 Maisonnette</a>，更是一例将黄铜运用于厨卫空间的范本之作。</p>\n<p>擅用黄铜的英国设计师 Tom Dixon 解释说，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2014/05/26/nostalgic-comfort-brings-brass-back-into-contemporary-design/\">黄铜最近很流行有可能是因其有一种“怀旧的舒适”的特质。</a></p>\n<p>最近，在慕尼黑新 Maxburg，一家名为 <a href=\"http://www.herzog.bar\">Herzog 的酒吧餐厅</a>开业，同样是巧用黄铜元素的佳作。这里最早是 16 世纪建成的 Maxburg 城堡，二战后被拆除，由建筑师  Sep Ruf 与 Theo Pabst 于 1957 年重新设计建造，成为慕尼黑标志性的现代主义建筑，亦是如今少数当地受保护的现代主义建筑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021629439w0gfzsmNiHrpuoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162943365jZWoThK1dmYzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>接手 Herzog 酒吧空间设计的是来自瑞士的 <a href=\"http://www.buildinc.ch\">Build Inc Architects 事务所</a>，目的是创造一个摩登的当代餐饮空间，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/02/build-inc-architects-herzog-bar-new-maxburg-restaurant-munchen-brass-munich/\">“整个项目最大的挑战在于，如何一边尊重当地建筑文化遗产，一边满足当代人对于美食空间的高标准需求。”</a></p>\n<p>黄铜元素成为整个空间设计的主线，14 条黄铜线组成的一条醒目的黄铜带从入口处的大理石地板延伸至吧台区域，并横向包裹了吧台立柱区域，又沿着一侧的墙壁向上攀沿至吧台顶部区域，给人一种连续的视觉体验。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162944WUCyNxT68AHBjLgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162945syMWrPu0tSIij7fD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>“这些黄铜纹理在酒吧里一点点铺开来，在灯光漫射的衬托下，使得整个空间显出温柔的气氛。”<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/02/build-inc-architects-herzog-bar-new-maxburg-restaurant-munchen-brass-munich/\">设计师说。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162945VyBAHfJTmIYzSZoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162946wvMYaDotFKny8Tgs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162946oEgUp1LfZzuw8QNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>除了吧台部分，黄铜还被用作外立面落地窗上的装饰，以及休闲沙发的底部框架，与吧台部分形成呼应。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162947HFnrpUJh1Vu5Aqk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162947czSsba1PI4BHmu5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162948l5HJDqosPiSyGLbx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>不过，Herzog 酒吧黄铜元素的脱颖而出多少要归功于墙壁与天花板的暗沉色调，从墙壁到天花板均被漆成了黑色，同样是黄铜质感的细长吊灯点亮了整个酒吧，也将随处可见的黄铜元素照亮，为 Herzog 创造出几分高雅却内敛的情调。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162949bkAR8J6LsEfd9MIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">卫生间</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162949JDALalhoSsxy3WIB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162950yGKeQaoXOcR9Ds3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162950RhIsc5JZ8zPv0GUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>相比之下，那个可能是全世界最喜欢用黄铜材质的 Tom Dixon ，用黄铜装饰的两家餐厅，看上去就略显浮夸。比如位于伦敦 Harrods 商场的三明治咖啡馆，以及位于巴黎的 Éclectic 餐厅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162951hQJZgGR7V209aFNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162951f1QwZF9bXNtLxkgh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">巴黎 Éclectic 餐厅</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162952Bmx2zG5AayerRthF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162952RVaGiJprc9PKH72M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">位于伦敦 Harrods 商场的三明治咖啡馆</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/02/build-inc-architects-herzog-bar-new-maxburg-restaurant-munchen-brass-munich/\">Dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.buildinc.ch/projekt-herzog-bar.html\">Build Inc Architects</a></p>\n\n"}